      "title": "GenAsset workflow notes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# GenAsset save workflow\n\n1. Open this workflow in ComfyUI.\n2. In **Save To GenAsset**, paste only the GenAsset `base_url`, `workspace_token`, and `asset_name`.\n3. Queue the workflow.\n\nThe image path is:\n\n`Checkpoint -> prompt encode -> KSampler -> VAE Decode -> Save To GenAsset -> SaveImage`\n\n`Save To GenAsset` auto-captures prompt text, negative prompt, checkpoint/model, KSampler seed, steps, cfg, sampler, scheduler, denoise, workflow JSON, image size, upstream node ids, and basic tags from the ComfyUI graph. If a field is not present in the graph, GenAsset saves it empty rather than blocking the run."
      ],
